  "texts": [
    "The five distinct labels attributed to CC/MCC are as follows: \"without CC/MCC\", \"with CC\", \"with MCC\", \"without MCC\", and \"not applicable\".",
    "As an example, in DRG code 53 of \"spinal disorders and injuries without CC/MCC,\" \"spinal disorders and injuries\" represents the base DRG label, while \"without CC/MCC\" serves as the CC/MCC label.",
    "Following this mapping process, the 738 DRG codes were converted into a combination of 340 base DRG labels each paired with one of the five CC/MCC labels.",
    "Results of the twolabel approach using DRG-LLaMA -7B with a maximum input token size of 512 was shown in Table 3.",
    "The top-1 prediction accuracy for base DRG and CC/MCC reached 67.8% and 67.5%, respectively."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}